Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫生靈之於人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙遠 低等而奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之凡俗獸禽草木大相徑庭者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此類異形 人類古來心有所懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謂之「蟲」 其時日不知幾多矣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾相依相偎 又於不覺間失去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無可替代的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此分享的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（提供）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩一個月了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\frz270\b0\fs60\pos(921,315)\fad(700,0)}蝕日之翳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 化野醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下個月的今天 好像會發生日食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽會被月亮的影子遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色會暗下來一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我認識的蟲師說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時蟲群會十分活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時平常看不到蟲的人也能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生你還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個蟲師又要來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他回信說有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是因為蟲都出來活動了才很忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他現在在哪做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些應該就是有關日食的全部記錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲之主要生態變化及應對之策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲喜日食妖光者眾 其力益增
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故中蟲氣者亦眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先例種種之可考者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其一 蟲柱也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲聚而成柱 不可於側近久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中蟲氣者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食過後 蟲柱片刻即散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘久聚不散 應行送蟲之儀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其二 畏光者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食過後 性情大變而畏光者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃食中為「夜陰」附體作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅蟲之藥需增以三分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其三 失眠者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久視蝕日而傷雙目者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日沒仍覺輝光不散而不能寐者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋「白暗」所致之異變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沐光脈之光或蟲生之光可愈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其四 失蹤者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食過後 下落不明者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯見於先天得視蟲者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為蟲所憑 與蟲共之山林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登高復現其形者眾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人眼不可視者亦常有也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有尚存人形者 唯同歸以情曉之可愈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然復返山林杳無音訊者亦多有也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多數先例都是蟲師們熟悉的蟲所致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次多半也不會出亂子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人擔憂的還是那種現象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦出現那樣的事態 不立即處理就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 流傳至今的記錄就只有這些了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若能從中預測到可能出現此種事態的地點便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然雲層有些厚 不過應該還能看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是銀古那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫他教我怎麼捉蟲 他卻淨寄這些藥來給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們跟大家都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他們今天有日食 但是不用慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有看久了會傷眼睛所以不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也別看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家想看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有這東西 所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真狡猾 就顧著自己一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我借我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個借我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我啦 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別搞壞了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您該到地下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不可接觸妖光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 我也想看看究竟是什麼模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的貴體不可有絲毫閃失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 願你們平安無事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧這些雲 正好能用肉眼看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這事小時候也發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就會恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊 那邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 看不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就又會出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你們要記住這種可怕的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記住 如果沒有太陽 我們是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒出過這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽又開始缺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還有奇怪的東西一直湊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 湊到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 升到天上 把那片影子越弄越大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什麼都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前幾天 這位…您怎麼稱呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蟲師銀古
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀古先生昨天找到我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近在日食時可能會出意外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果確實發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過處理此事需要各位的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮住太陽的那片黑影中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種名為「蝕日」的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠會吸引四周的小蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令其增殖而形成黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種蟲平時潛伏於地底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯獨在日食時會分為「核」與「根」兩部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核升上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若想消除黑影 就要找到「蝕日」在大地上的根
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其曝於陽光之下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此 眼下只知道牠的根就在這個村莊附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能把有異狀的地方全都挖開一一確認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這麼說 也不知道該怎麼找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那種地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這兒乾瞪眼也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如分頭找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 請繼續找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是一點發現也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好到了明天 太陽又會像往常那樣出現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食已安然過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往其他「蝕日」可能出現之地的蟲師們也都報來平安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那裡的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大白天就這麼暗啊 真晦氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你那邊有發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有什麼根嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都幾天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都沒什麼不對勁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你快說說那根長什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按記載 根的所在地和形態每次都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位的不安我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但還請耐著性子踏踏實實地找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們怎麼信你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這麼下去 水田旱田就都要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不想辦法屯點糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個冬天就別想熬過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去存在於日常生活的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從未想過會失去的東西時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們究竟該何去何從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又該倚靠何物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色這麼暗還關得嚴嚴實實？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去不像空屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白髮 白膚 淺淡的瞳仁 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你做什麼呢 現在還是白天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太陽不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我也就能出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的頭髮…你也病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麼會長成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我不怕陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出門不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的 你看 什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去看看你之前說的花田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 田裡的莊稼都枯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得進城賣點東西才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心又長斑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的斑 是像黑色斑點那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是村長帶來的那個蟲師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑斑 又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說製造這片黑影的蟲的亞種
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這種病的病因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子的病能治好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 至今還沒有發現治療的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 能把前因後果告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽了你剛才的話 我想起一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子剛懷上那兩個孩子不久時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了和這次日食一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過當時是月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快看 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時的月亮就和這次日食一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸地被黑影遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總覺得很不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不知道為什麼 突然沒了知覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來 妻子平安生下了兩個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其中一個卻是白膚白髮 瞳色也十分淺淡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 妻子的身體一直沒能恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久便去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和的黑斑過了好幾天才消退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期間一直發著高燒 臥病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕照到一絲陽光 黑斑就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以白天必須得把所有的門窗都關緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 日和就幾乎沒出過家門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人在裡屋生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您和夫人看到的月食應該是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是「蝕日」的亞種「蝕月」所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孕婦若被偽月食的光所照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胎兒便會喪失色素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生後一旦照到陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便會產生如灼傷一般的斑點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的其中一個孩子之所以能平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為腹中的另一個孩子擋住了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而免於被光所照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和保護了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會盡可能設法治療日和姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您協助我化解這場日食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向就可以去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你病了 照到陽光可能就會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 你喜歡的東西這裡都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我想和日向在外面玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 外面有好多漂亮的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了一個開著很多花的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只有我知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有太陽的時候去肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好晃眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說過多少遍了 為什麼不聽話！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再跟日和說會讓她想出門的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只會讓她更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我摘些花田裡的花來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 我分不清那個地方在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次給她穿這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你不在就沒意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟日和在一起我更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是那麼喜歡到外面去玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只有自己能出去所以覺得很愧疚？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很可憐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想別人這麼看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那…我該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我換啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來跟我換啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…要怎麼換？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到的話 就不要再讓我看見你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就忍不住會想 本來我也應該和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 飯菜我放門外了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸有話要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你的病因
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和製造這次日食的傢伙類似的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還沒有辦法治療吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們剛才說的 我都聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 只要解除日食
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定有一天能找到治好你的門路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和日向要幫助這位銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就委屈你一個人待一陣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道多少年沒在白天出門了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過曬不到太陽 大家就變得那麼消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.72,0:25:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們肯定也能多少體會到我的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真暢快
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食就這樣持續下去多好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.82,0:25:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向說過的花田是在這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時走到了這附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.29,0:26:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後日向就把我背回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山路這麼崎嶇 她當時一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.80,0:26:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.33,0:26:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.92,0:26:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.80,0:26:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮 是什麼花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.59,0:27:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 就跟日向說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.57,0:27:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能和日向一起看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.67,0:27:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快讓他別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.54,0:27:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是讓人更慌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子也餓壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.51,0:27:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又出門了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.60,0:27:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.27,0:27:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.10,0:27:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這花是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.57,0:27:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼怎麼回事 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.98,0:28:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開著一大片 可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.40,0:28:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這花不應該開在這個時節
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.62,0:28:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為「蝕日」的根就在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.79,0:28:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我那個地方在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.84,0:28:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果繼續放任「蝕日」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影就會越來越大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食的範圍也會擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.38,0:28:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲群橫生的不毛之地將越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.35,0:28:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不盡快處理就無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.56,0:28:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對我來說 這樣下去更好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和其他人並沒有什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.48,0:28:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要吃東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你並不直接接觸太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.99,0:28:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你如何憎恨太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.74,0:28:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命依然是由陽光維持的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.45,0:28:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那種蟲 真是一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.08,0:28:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「蝕日」這種蟲只有在日食期間才能來到地表
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外就只能潛伏在地底深處
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.97,0:29:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 牠為什麼要來到地面上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些蟲終生在黑暗中生活 並不需要陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.64,0:29:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「蝕日」之所以來到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.85,0:29:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為牠需要陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.52,0:29:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許牠僅僅待在地底是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.32,0:29:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 牠的根只要一照到陽光就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.49,0:29:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才由核的部分吸引蟲群製造黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.12,0:29:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承受陽光的同時又保護根部免受光照
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.50,0:29:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其實也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.71,0:29:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就連置身這個幽暗的世界 你都感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.72,0:29:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.84,0:29:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你擺脫不了待在那個門窗緊閉的小房間裡的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的這點幽光也會被黑暗吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「其中一個孩子之所以能平安無事」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「是因為腹中的另一個孩子擋住了她」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.58,0:30:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「而免於被光所照吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你來跟我換啊！」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.83,0:30:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不要再讓我看見你」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.76,0:30:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有我就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.85,0:30:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:30:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你看到日向了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.21,0:31:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.08,0:31:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.05,0:31:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定在山裡出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.55,0:31:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願別是因為日食的影響而消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.34,0:31:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾會有人在日食期間失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.26,0:31:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有些人會變得只有看得見蟲的人才能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.85,0:31:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得見蟲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.98,0:31:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.23,0:31:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定很快就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.95,0:31:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.24,0:31:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.32,0:31:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.29,0:31:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都三天了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.67,0:31:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.89,0:32:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.23,0:32:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.91,0:32:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是真心不想看見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.75,0:32:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.42,0:32:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒想過太陽會消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得天天都有日出是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.68,0:32:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 就是因為我覺得日向肯定不會離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.85,0:32:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會說出那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.52,0:32:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 日向就像是太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.94,0:32:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.57,0:32:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:32:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.91,0:33:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.46,0:33:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.84,0:33:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.56,0:33:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.86,0:33:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.07,0:33:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.91,0:33:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再說那些過分的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.38,0:33:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.55,0:33:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變回小時候那個溫柔開朗的日向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.56,0:34:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀古先生 我找到日向了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.82,0:34:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經變成普通人看不見的模樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.41,0:34:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀古先生 怎麼做才能讓日向恢復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.33,0:34:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要根除「蝕日」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.79,0:34:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣蟲群就會散去 影響也會減輕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著 你要一直陪在她身邊 耐心地和她說話
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.90,0:34:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡 根應該就在這下面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.95,0:35:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把土挖開
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.46,0:35:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.59,0:35:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.96,0:35:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.76,0:35:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是根
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.93,0:35:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把牠搬到能曬到太陽的地方就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.27,0:35:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.35,0:35:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.69,0:35:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那片山坡上照得到太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.91,0:35:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.13,0:35:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 山坡都翻過去了 怎麼還跑不出那片影子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.84,0:36:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影追過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.14,0:36:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.23,0:36:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道男人們怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.77,0:36:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願他們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.57,0:36:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.53,0:36:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.24,0:36:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光…！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.55,0:36:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 陽光回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.80,0:36:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.43,0:36:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這樣就又能活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不晃眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.73,0:36:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.65,0:37:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.95,0:37:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曬到太陽也沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.71,0:37:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把勁 再加把勁就能擺脫黑影了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.10,0:37:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.14,0:37:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把蓋子打開
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.37,0:37:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.25,0:38:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們看天上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.55,0:38:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子散了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.10,0:38:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲 萬歲 萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.19,0:38:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.45,0:38:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.41,0:38:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.21,0:38:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 「蝕日」製造的妖光的波長通常對人有害
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.39,0:38:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對受「蝕月」影響的人則有益
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.22,0:38:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.77,0:38:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.31,0:39:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這個你就不需要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.44,0:39:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是「蝕日」的核的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.07,0:39:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它具有活化生命的強大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.20,0:39:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得妥善使用也能帶來益處
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.33,0:39:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就給日向吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.46,0:39:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 你不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然她對你的話有這麼清晰的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.76,0:39:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼恢復原狀也就是時間問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.10,0:39:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 你就好好陪著她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.73,0:39:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.27,0:39:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次該輪到我來照耀日向了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.86,0:39:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該怎麼處理這東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.87,0:40:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你現在才來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.17,0:40:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子 這次你又沒能如願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 結果還是看不到蟲！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.51,0:40:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食就正常開始 很快又正常結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.59,0:40:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有發生！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.06,0:40:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是再好不過了 平安無事是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.31,0:40:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 話是這麼說啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.60,0:40:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來求醫的人是不是多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.86,0:40:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 太陽重新出現之後
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.11,0:40:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有些怕光和睡不著覺的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 治好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.74,0:40:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 藥我是開了 但是都不見好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.87,0:40:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫的信你都沒看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.71,0:40:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是蟲造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.05,0:40:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我寄給你的包裹裡的藥就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.97,0:40:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:41:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待會兒我要問你日食的時候都幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.31,0:41:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.68,0:41:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.27,0:41:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到一個地方去彙報當時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.56,0:41:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一會兒總可以吧 別走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.69,0:41:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.79,0:41:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.58,0:41:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀古修書來報
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.62,0:41:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已順利收場
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.59,0:41:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.92,0:41:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 他近期會前來彙報
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.43,0:41:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是還有一物想請小姐過目
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.81,0:41:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說的話可不怎麼靠得住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.77,0:41:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 就耐心等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.16,0:42:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.93,0:42:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 天氣真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.23,0:42:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願今天也能平安無事
